  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, combine the oxtail, rice vinegar, fish sauce, lime juice, sugar, ginger, cinnamon, star anise, black pepper, cumin, and paprika.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil over high heat, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 2 hours, or until the oxtail is tender.",
    "Strain the broth through a fine-mesh sieve into a clean pot, discarding the solids.",
    "Add the water to the pot and bring the broth to a boil over high heat.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Cook the rice noodles according to the package instructions.",
    "To assemble the dish, place some noodles in a bowl, then add some oxtail and a portion of the broth.",
    "Garnish with beansprouts, cilantro, mint, jalapeño, and scallions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
